claim.claim-text:
1. A method of manufacturing a strain detector, comprising: 
applying a metal-glaze-based paste over an insulating substrate at a position where a strain-resistance element is to be disposed; 
forming a strain-resistance element at said position; 
forming a power electrode, output electrodes, a ground electrode, and a circuit pattern over said insulating substrate; 
disposing a temperature-characteristic-compensation element over said insulating substrate; and 
forming a first protective layer over said strain-resistance element.
